// ━━━ Developer Profile System ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// This is the self-service authenticated developer profile.
// Separate from the `developers` table (which is admin-seeded static content).
// A `developers` row is only created/linked AFTER kycStatus=VERIFIED AND profileCompletion=100%.

enum DeveloperKycStatus {
  PENDING
  UNDER_REVIEW
  VERIFIED
  REJECTED
}

enum DeveloperOnboardingStatus {
  REGISTERED
  EMAIL_VERIFIED
  PROFILE_INCOMPLETE
  PROFILE_COMPLETED
  DOCUMENTS_UPLOADED
  UNDER_REVIEW
  APPROVED
  REJECTED
  SUSPENDED
}

enum DeveloperSubscriptionPlan {
  FREE
  PROFESSIONAL
  ENTERPRISE
}

enum DeveloperDocumentType {
  RERA_CERTIFICATE
  GST_CERTIFICATE
  PAN_CARD
  REGISTRATION_CERTIFICATE
  AUTHORIZED_PERSON_ID
  COMPANY_LOGO
  BROCHURE
  OTHER
}

enum DeveloperNotificationType {
  NEW_LEAD
  PROJECT_APPROVED
  PROJECT_REJECTED
  BROCHURE_DOWNLOADED
  PROFILE_VERIFIED
  PROJECT_FEATURED
  ADMIN_MESSAGE
  SUBSCRIPTION_EXPIRY
}

model DeveloperProfile {
  id                     String                    @id @default(uuid())
  userId                 String                    @unique @map("user_id")
  user                   User                      @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  // Link to the `developers` table row — only set AFTER kycStatus=VERIFIED AND profileCompletion=100%
  // Admin can link to an existing `developers` row or trigger auto-creation of a new one.
  linkedDeveloperId      String?                   @map("linked_developer_id") @db.Text
  linkedDeveloper        Developer?                @relation(fields: [linkedDeveloperId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  // ── Company Basics (Step 1 of onboarding) ──────────────────────────────────
  companyName            String?                   @map("company_name")
  slug                   String?                   @unique
  description            String?                   @db.Text
  shortDescription       String?                   @map("short_description")
  logo                   String?                   // CloudFront URL
  logoS3Key              String?                   @map("logo_s3_key")
  banner                 String?                   // CloudFront URL
  bannerS3Key            String?                   @map("banner_s3_key")
  website                String?
  foundedYear            Int?                      @map("founded_year")
  headquarters           String?
  countriesServed        String[]                  @default([]) @map("countries_served")
  totalEmployees         Int?                      @map("total_employees")
  yearsExperience        Int?                      @map("years_experience")

  // ── Legal & Verification (Step 2 of onboarding) ────────────────────────────
  reraNumber             String?                   @map("rera_number")
  gstNumber              String?                   @map("gst_number")
  panNumber              String?                   @map("pan_number")

  // ── Business Information (Step 3 of onboarding) ────────────────────────────
  projectTypesFocus      String[]                  @default([]) @map("project_types_focus")
  // e.g. ["RESIDENTIAL","COMMERCIAL","VILLA","LUXURY","AFFORDABLE","MIXED_USE"]
  citiesServed           String[]                  @default([]) @map("cities_served")

  // ── Social Links ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  instagramUrl           String?                   @map("instagram_url")
  linkedinUrl            String?                   @map("linkedin_url")
  facebookUrl            String?                   @map("facebook_url")
  youtubeUrl             String?                   @map("youtube_url")
  twitterUrl             String?                   @map("twitter_url")
  whatsapp               String?
  telegram               String?

  // ── Phone (for OTP auth, matches Agent pattern) ────────────────────────────
  phone                  String?
  phoneCountryCode       String?                   @map("phone_country_code")

  // ── Status & KYC ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  onboardingStatus       DeveloperOnboardingStatus @default(REGISTERED) @map("onboarding_status")
  kycStatus              DeveloperKycStatus        @default(PENDING) @map("kyc_status")
  isVerified             Boolean                   @default(false) @map("is_verified")
  isFeatured             Boolean                   @default(false) @map("is_featured")
  featuredRank           Int?                      @map("featured_rank")

  // ── Profile Completion Score ────────────────────────────────────────────────
  // Total: Company(20) + Verification(25) + Business(20) + Media(20) + Social(5) + Projects(10) = 100
  profileCompletion      Int                       @default(0) @map("profile_completion")
  completionCompany      Int                       @default(0) @map("completion_company")       // max 20
  completionVerification Int                       @default(0) @map("completion_verification")  // max 25
  completionBusiness     Int                       @default(0) @map("completion_business")      // max 20
  completionMedia        Int                       @default(0) @map("completion_media")         // max 20
  completionSocial       Int                       @default(0) @map("completion_social")        // max 5
  completionProjects     Int                       @default(0) @map("completion_projects")      // max 10

  // ── Subscription ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  subscriptionPlan       DeveloperSubscriptionPlan @default(FREE) @map("subscription_plan")
  subscriptionExpiresAt  DateTime?                 @map("subscription_expires_at")

  // ── Analytics Counters (denormalized for performance) ──────────────────────
  totalLeadsReceived     Int                       @default(0) @map("total_leads_received")
  totalProjectViews      Int                       @default(0) @map("total_project_views")
  totalProjectsPublished Int                       @default(0) @map("total_projects_published")

  // ── Admin Fields ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  approvedBy             String?                   @map("approved_by")
  approvedAt             DateTime?                 @map("approved_at")
  rejectionReason        String?                   @db.Text @map("rejection_reason")
  suspendedAt            DateTime?                 @map("suspended_at")
  suspendedBy            String?                   @map("suspended_by")

  // Admin-provided match suggestion during verification
  // Stores suggested existing developer IDs from fuzzy name matching
  adminMatchSuggestions  Json?                     @map("admin_match_suggestions")

  // ── AIDeveloper™ Score ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
  AIDeveloperScore    Int?                      @map("AI_developer_score")
  AIScoreBreakdown    Json?                     @map("AI_score_breakdown")
  AIScoredAt          DateTime?                 @map("AI_scored_at")

  // ── Relations ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  documents              DeveloperDocument[]
  notifications          DeveloperNotification[]
  projects               Project[]                 // Projects owned by this profile (Phase 1)
  leads                  Lead[]                    // CRM leads routed to this developer profile

  createdAt              DateTime                  @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt              DateTime                  @updatedAt @map("updated_at")

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([onboardingStatus])
  @@index([kycStatus])
  @@index([isVerified])
  @@index([isFeatured, featuredRank])
  @@index([profileCompletion])
  @@index([linkedDeveloperId])
  @@index([subscriptionPlan])
  @@map("developer_profiles")
}

model DeveloperDocument {
  id                   String                  @id @default(uuid())
  developerProfileId   String                  @map("developer_profile_id")
  developerProfile     DeveloperProfile        @relation(fields: [developerProfileId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  type                 DeveloperDocumentType   @map("document_type")
  fileUrl              String                  @map("file_url")   // CloudFront URL
  s3Key                String?                 @map("s3_key")
  fileName             String?                 @map("file_name")
  mimeType             String?                 @map("mime_type")
  sizeBytes            Int?                    @map("size_bytes")

  status               DocumentStatus          @default(PENDING)
  reviewedBy           String?                 @map("reviewed_by")
  reviewedAt           DateTime?               @map("reviewed_at")
  rejectionReason      String?                 @db.Text @map("rejection_reason")

  createdAt            DateTime                @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt            DateTime                @updatedAt @map("updated_at")

  @@unique([developerProfileId, type])
  @@index([developerProfileId])
  @@index([status])
  @@index([type])
  @@map("developer_documents")
}

model DeveloperNotification {
  id                   String                      @id @default(uuid())
  developerProfileId   String                      @map("developer_profile_id")
  developerProfile     DeveloperProfile            @relation(fields: [developerProfileId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  type                 DeveloperNotificationType
  title                String
  message              String                      @db.Text
  isRead               Boolean                     @default(false) @map("is_read")
  metadata             Json?                       // e.g. { projectId, leadId, amount }

  createdAt            DateTime                    @default(now()) @map("created_at")

  @@index([developerProfileId, isRead])
  @@index([developerProfileId, createdAt])
  @@index([type])
  @@map("developer_notifications")
}
